{
  "text": "Skirt has extended toward the left hand, but somewhat shorter toward the right. There is a black bag hanging from the belt of the entity on the left side. It seems to me that this black bag has a meaning of the acquiring of material possessions and wealth as a part of the left-hand path. Draw a comment on that. I am well although this meaning was not intended by Ra as part of this a complex of a concept. We find the interpretation quite acceptable. As we observe a law in the questioning, we shall take this opportunity to say that the level of transferred energy dwindles rapidly, and we would offer the opportunity for one more before a question at this a working if it is a desire to have a lot of people.",
